                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-204-off1072 t18220417-204-cd1073"></join>, the sum of 3 l. 3 s. 3 1/2 d. in monies numbered, which he had received on account of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-204-victim1867" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Clark
                        <interp inst="t18220417-204-victim1867" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
